ğŸš« Common Mistakes

âŒ Storing values instead of indices

âŒ Forgetting to remove out-of-window elements

âŒ Using priority_queue â†’ gives O(n log k) (still accepted but not optimal)

ğŸ§  Easy Memory Trick

â€œDeque front = answer, back = clean smaller valuesâ€
